<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to the KTBlog Newsletter!</title>
  <!--[if mso]>
  <noscript>
    <xml>
      <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
      </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
    </xml>
  </noscript>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f6f9;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f6f9;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #1E4DB7; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff;">KTBlog</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Welcome Banner -->
          <tr>
            <td>
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E4DB7 0%, #3B6FD4 100%); padding: 32px; text-align: center;">
                    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 26px; color: #ffffff;">You're In!</h2>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-size: 16px;">Welcome to the KTBlog Newsletter</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">Hello {{name}},</p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">Thank you for subscribing to the KTBlog newsletter! We're excited to have you join our community of readers, thinkers, and creators.</p>

              <!-- Benefits -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f8f9fb; border-radius: 8px; margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 24px;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a2e;">What to Expect:</h3>
                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">
                          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                              <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-right: 12px;">
                                <div style="background-color: #1E4DB7; border-radius: 50%; width: 22px; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px;">&#10003;</div>
                              </td>
                              <td style="color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Curated Articles:</strong> Handpicked content on topics that matter</td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">
                          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                              <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-right: 12px;">
                                <div style="background-color: #1E4DB7; border-radius: 50%; width: 22px; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px;">&#10003;</div>
                              </td>
                              <td style="color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><strong>New Post Alerts:</strong> Be the first to read new articles</td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">
                          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                              <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-right: 12px;">
                                <div style="background-color: #1E4DB7; border-radius: 50%; width: 22px; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px;">&#10003;</div>
                              </td>
                              <td style="color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Exclusive Content:</strong> Access subscriber-only insights and guides</td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">
                          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                              <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-right: 12px;">
                                <div style="background-color: #1E4DB7; border-radius: 50%; width: 22px; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px;">&#10003;</div>
                              </td>
                              <td style="color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Community Updates:</strong> Stay connected with what's happening</td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">We respect your inbox and promise to only send you valuable content. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>

              <!-- CTA -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{blogUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #1E4DB7; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Start Reading</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">Stay tuned for our next edition!</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">The KTBlog Team</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">&copy; {{year}} KTBlog. All rights reserved.</p>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #1E4DB7; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px;">
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}" style="color: #9ca3af; text-decoration: underline;">Unsubscribe</a> from our newsletter.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
